<main class="container review-detail-page"><div class="breadcrumb nav-title"><span class="active">任务三：三栏式布局（<a href="/task/detail?taskId=3">查看详情</a>）</span></div><div class="main"><div class="submit-group-info"><h4>团队：<a href="/group/profile?groupId=2967" target="_blank">js高手之路</a></h4><p class="submit-basic"><span class="submit-time"><a href="/user/profile?userId=7842">倪振胜</a>&nbsp;更新于<em>03-29 16:00</em></span><span class="review-num">已经有<em>2</em>人 review</span><span class="score">平均得分：<em>9</em></span></p><p>代码地址：<a href="https://github.com/jshacker007/ife2016/tree/master/stage1/task3" target="_blank">https://github.com/jshacker007/ife2016/tree/master/stage1/task3</a></p><p>demo：<a href="http://jshacker007.github.io/ife2016/stage1/task3/index.html" target="_blank">http://jshacker007.github.io/ife2016/stage1/task3/index.html</a></p><p class="submit-descr">通常简单的做法是在html中采用左栏-右栏-中栏的顺序定义，实现简单。这里保持了html中左栏-中栏-右栏的顺序，实现上使用了margin-right为负值的情况</p></div><ul class="review-result-list container-fluid"><li class="row review-result" data-id="1560"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=3995" target="_blank">前端后端傻傻分得清楚</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-30 10:10</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=10412" target="_blank">曾煜</a>&nbsp;03-30 10:10&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">8</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">总体很好，但是有一个小遗憾。<br />
当调整浏览器窗口大小时，布局的内容会自动调整，但是没有为justwrap设置一个min-width，当页面的宽度过小时，左右两栏的内容会将中间一栏的宽度挤压为0，继续缩小则左栏会覆盖到右栏。<br />
设置min-width后，浏览器窗口大小小雨min-width时，页面的内容不会继续缩小，浏览器将提供一个滚动条。</span><ul class="reply-wrap"><li class="reply"style="display:block;" data-id=643><p class="reply-info">作者<a href="/user/profile?userId=7842">倪振胜</a>&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<span class="time">03-31 10:59</span></p><p class="reply-content">感谢review！很好的建议！</p></li></ul></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="1548"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=1376" target="_blank">ife</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-30 00:09</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=3128" target="_blank">罗尖</a>&nbsp;03-30 00:09&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">10</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">提供了一个新方法，保留了html的顺序，学习一下！</span></div></li></ul><div class="review-page-wrap" data-total="2" data-page-size="10" data-page-no="1"></div></div></main>
